data.description: Don't miss out on this three bed, two bath home in Sheldons View Subdivision. This home offers an open floor plan, spacious living area with gas fireplace and built-ins. Charming kitchen with breakfast bar and dining area. Primary bedroom offers a private bath with a jetted tub, separate shower and two walk-in closets. The two additional bedrooms are spacious and offer carpet and large closets. The sunroom just off of the main living area is the perfect place to enjoy your morning coffee. Exterior amenities include a two car garage and privacy fence. Call a local REALTOR to schedule your showing TODAY!
